Package: scDDboost
Type: Package
Title: Identifying differential distributed genes for single cell RNA data
Version: 2.0
Date: 2017-11-11
Author: Xiuyu Ma
Maintainer: Xiuyu Ma
     <watsonforfun@gmail.com>
Description: modal cluster selecting genes for measuring similarities between cells, mixture double dirichlet prior combining with empirical bayesian method to find differential distributed genes.
